flowchart LR
    Producers([Producers])
    Consumers([Consumer Group])
    Broker1[Kafka Broker 1<br/>P0 Leader, P1 Replica]
    Broker2[Kafka Broker 2<br/>P1 Leader, P2 Replica]
    Broker3[Kafka Broker 3<br/>P2 Leader, P0 Replica]
    Log[("Partition Logs<br/>(append-only,<br/>segmented)")]
    Coord[KRaft / ZooKeeper<br/>broker registry,<br/>leader election]

    Producers -->|send key,value| Broker1
    Producers -->|send| Broker2
    Producers -->|send| Broker3
    Broker1 <-->|replicate ISR| Broker2
    Broker2 <-->|replicate ISR| Broker3
    Broker1 --> Log
    Broker2 --> Log
    Broker3 --> Log
    Consumers -->|pull batches<br/>commit offsets| Broker1
    Consumers -->|pull| Broker2
    Consumers -->|pull| Broker3
    Coord -.->|metadata, election| Broker1
    Coord -.->|metadata, election| Broker2
    Coord -.->|metadata, election| Broker3

